enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve setting or interpreting error codes.
Setting the error class is a prerequisite for determining the error code, which is used in getDefaultReasonPhrase.
Setting the error number is a prerequisite for determining the error code, which is used in getDefaultReasonPhrase.
The error code obtained from getErrorCode() is directly used in getDefaultReasonPhrase() to determine the reason phrase.
The error class obtained from getErrorClass() is indirectly used in getDefaultReasonPhrase() through the error code.
The error number obtained from getErrorNumber() is indirectly used in getDefaultReasonPhrase() through the error code.
